      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like everything i ever made was just a lie. i look at my studio and it just feels like a graveyard of things that don't matter anymore. there's nothing left in me. no more colors, no more ideas... just this massive, empty silence. it feels like i've already finished my story and i'm just waiting for the credits to roll.",
