    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so exhausting. i look at my hands and they feel so heavy, like they don't even belong to me anymore. i'm just going through the motions of breathing because i'm supposed to, but it feels like i'm just taking up space that could be used for something else. if there's no more art to make, what's the point in staying? isn't it just more kind to stop when the purpose is gone?",
